 Canadian cultural production about the Spanish Civil War (spanishcivilwar.ca), directed by Bart Vautour and Emily Robins Sharpe.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh1 aSharpe, Emily Robins, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVautour, Bart, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVautour, Bart, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2015z978311127402708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2015z978311127703540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780776621654423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780776621654/original  a978-3-11-127402-7  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2015b2015  a978-3-11-127703-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2015b2015  aGBV-deGruyter-alles